channel.title: Void Elite Model invisible. IVE BROKEN THESEARCH BAR!
channel.description: So i downloaded void elite models. added in item.cfg and added the ints, ok everything is fine. I spawn the items the robe bottom spawns but inventory model is invisible and when i wield it equips in the bodyslot and its invisible in the body slot too plus the void top spawns perfectly but when equiped it equips in the legsslot. The puzzling this is that when only one of item of the set is equiped it looks fucked up on ur character but when both of them r equiped they equip properly but when u relog it shits up ur account(but still in the wrong slots).
